ng Loops</a></strong></h3>\r\n<p><a href="https://techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Hacking-LOOPS.jpg" data-wpel-link="internal"><img src="https://techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Hacking-LOOPS.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" srcset="//techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Hacking-LOOPS.jpg 640w, //techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Hacking-LOOPS-300x194.jpg 300w" alt="Hacking Loops" width="640" height="414" data-ll-status="loaded" /></a></p>\r\n<p>It is a great place to start learning to hack. Here, you can also set up your own pentest/hacking lab. The free guide delivered to your email that will show you step-by-step how to get started and set up your own lab today.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>10. <a href="http://www.metasploit.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow external" data-wpel-link="external">MetaSploit</a></strong></h3>\r\n<p><a href="https://techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Metasploit.jpg" data-wpel-link="internal"><img src="https://techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Metasploit.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 651px) 100vw, 651px" srcset="//techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Metasploit.jpg 651w, //techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Metasploit-300x153.jpg 300w" alt="MetaSploit" width="651" height="333" data-ll-status="loaded" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Well, MetaSploit is one of the world&rsquo;s most popular Penetration Testing software which already helped lots of organizations to improve their security. The Metasploit blog will be a great place to start. Get access to information, free tools, tutorials, and more. So, MetaSploit is another best site to learn to hack.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>11. <a href="http://sectools.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow external" data-wpel-link="external">SecTools</a></strong></h3>\r\n<p><a href="https://techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/SecTools.png" data-wpel-link="internal"><img src="https://techviral.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/SecTools.p